latestIgtvVideos.caption: TIL that Joe Johnston (the legendary director of Rocketeer, Jumanji and Captain America among other things) redesigned the iconic Star Wars logo to the one we know and love in literally one day. Can’t believe I got to sit in the audience and listen to this story. In general, this was an excellent panel about the early days of Industrial Light and Magic. Other legends on the panel included Lawrence Kasdan, Ron Howard, Dennis Muren, and Phil Tippett (who was also hilarious). #StarWarsCelebration
